transcripts: Hey guys my name is Jayson I'm a senior product developer transport and today I'm going to be walking through some really cool product today we're going to take a look at the Austin pack it's a 26 liter pack made out of a 600 denier polyester and on the bottom here you have a synthetic leather this material is also found on the lashing score and on these trim touch points here all right let's start with the back panel you have a padded back panel padded straps and a webbing handle on the top this is a one compartment bag so getting into the main compartment you have a 15 inch laptop sleeves on front of the bag you have three different storage options one you have a vertical zippered here that gives you access to a flat pocket great for stashing your tablet or your notebook or some books smaller zippered pocket on the top for your wallet or sunglasses and on the bottom a small zippered pocket for stashing anything else want to carry this pocket also has an organizer a one pocket organizer here and two slots for your pens or pencils right so that's it for the Austin pack this bag is guaranteed for life.
